query:
SELECT DISTINCT
    h.haul_id AS "haul_id!: HaulId",
    h.message_id,
    h.start_timestamp,
    h.stop_timestamp
FROM
    hauls h
    LEFT JOIN hauls_matrix m ON h.haul_id = m.haul_id
WHERE
    (
        m.haul_distribution_status IS NULL
        OR m.haul_distribution_status = $1
    )
    AND h.total_living_weight > 0
    AND h.fiskeridir_vessel_id = $2
